    h1 Installation
    ul.docs-index

    h2 Framework7 CLI
    p The most recommended way to start with new Framework7 app is to use <a href="https://framework7.io/cli/">Framework7 CLI</a>, it provides most complete amount of combinations with different templates, target devices/platforms, frameworks and some of best practices.

    h2 Ready To Use Templates
    p You can also check the #[a(href="https://framework7.io/templates/") starter app templates and tools] section to start straight away from some pre-setup app.

    h2 Manual Installation
    p We can download/install framework7 with few ways:
    ul
      li
        p
          b Download From GitHub Repository
        p We can download required Framework7 files from <a href="https://github.com/framework7io/framework7/releases">Framework7 GitHub repository</a>.
      li
        p
          b Install From NPM
        p We can also install Framework7 from NPM:
        :code
          $ npm install framework7
    p From the downloaded Core package we will need files from <code>css</code> and <code>js</code> folders


